      "text": "On July 10, 1941, the Jewish residents of Jedwabne were forced into a barn and burned alive by their own Polish neighbors during the Nazi occupation. It's a dark chapter, and one we should not run from. \n\nThat's why I'm deeply troubled to see 85 years later the memorial for this https://t.co/X7y0CLN0nY",
