      "text": "Happy 63rd birthday to the city of @CoralSpringsFL! It's the honor of a lifetime to serve this community in Congress, and a daily privilege to have one of my district offices right inside City Hall.\n\nHere's to 63 years and many more of a city that keeps getting better every year! https://t.co/kJ4XDIkTqB",
