      "text": "Our community deserves peace of mind that when they call 911, someone on the other end will always answer.\n \nThat's why I secured $1,031,000 for Coconut Creek to build a reliable network so police and fire dispatch stay online even during outages and emergencies. \n \nIn a https://t.co/dnekSQP59a",
