      "text": "A railroad crossing is not just a piece of infrastructure. It connects neighborhoods, and for too long, Boca Raton has been disconnected because of the downed Jeffery Street crossing. \n \nI was proud to fix this by delivering $2M to Boca Raton to rebuild the crossing and reconnect https://t.co/gNLi6fd3Gk",
