      "text": "Independence Day is a day we honor the patriots who made this country what it is. It's also a reminder that from the very beginning, freedom has never been free. The American experiment is a promise, one every American has to help keep. \n\nTo the families across South Florida who https://t.co/7pUSeVnVee",
