      "profileHref": "/country/usa/congress/jared-moskowitz",
      "text": "This is a promising step, but we still need @secrubio and @secwar to deploy hospital ships (not warships) to help the people of Venezuela. \n\nHospital ships are designed to hold up to 1,000 patient beds and have dozens of fully equipped operating rooms. Details matter in emergency",
