      "countryId": "usa",
      "profileHref": "/country/usa/congress/jared-moskowitz",
      "text": "Across South Florida, countless families are grieving for the lives lost in Venezuela. The United States can and should do all we can to help those suffering, and we can deploying one of our Navy hospital ships. \n\nI appreciate @WPLGLocal10 for their time and urge @SecRubio and https://t.co/jfCymObQwN",
