      "countryId": "usa",
      "profileHref": "/country/usa/congress/jared-moskowitz",
      "text": "As the situation in Venezuela continues to worsen, I continue to call on @SecRubio and @SecWar to deploy the USNS Comfort or Mercy to save lives. These Navy hospital ships can make a real difference. In emergency management, every hour counts. We can't afford to wait.",
