      "profileHref": "/country/usa/congress/jared-moskowitz",
      "text": "The Supreme Court got this one right. \n\nFor more than 150 years, birthright citizenship has been settled law that's made the United States a stronger, more welcoming place. That's a promise worth protecting. If you're born here, you belong here, and today the Court agreed.",
      "createdAt": "2026-06-30T15:24:21Z",
